		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Tumbling Opportunist",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "free"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong> Your most recent action was to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.21WIfSu7Xd7uKqV8]{Tumble Through} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.jfsmtOx4QgXB19BL]{Tumbling Strike}, and you successfully moved through an enemy's space.</p><hr><p>You use a burst of stamina to perform a breathtaking feat of Acrobatics as you speed through a foe's space, leaving your foe lying flat on their back. You attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ge56Lu1xXVFYUnLP]{Trip} the enemy whose space you moved through. You can use [[/act trip skill=acrobatics]]{Acrobatics} instead of Athletics for this check.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
